tabs.tab_content: Clear up asphalt, construction sites or walkways with this industrial street sweeper. This outdoor sweeper uses tough bristles and offers more standard features, such as joystick controls for brush functions, front disc brakes, high-capacity fuel and hydraulic tanks, and shut-off valves for changing the hydraulic oil filters. Joystick control and shifting on the go are also available.
